<lb ed="W" n="0352a03"/><milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a04"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a05"/><div1 type="other"><mulu type="其他" level="1" label="錄文三"/><head>〔錄文三〕</head>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a06"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a07"/><p id="pW07p0352a0701" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">玄奘法師禮拜，逐月有十齋日：</p>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a08"/><list><item id="itemW07p0352a0801">一<note n="0352001" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「一」，底本作「十一」，據甲本刪。</note>日齋<note n="0352002" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「齋」，底本缺，甲本作「有」，據文意補。</note>，善惡童子下界，念定光佛；</item>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a09"/><item id="itemW07p0352a0901">八日齋，太子下界，念藥師琉璃光佛；</item>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a10"/><item id="itemW07p0352a1001">十四日齋<note n="0352003" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「齋」，底、甲本缺，據文意補。</note>，司命下界，念賢劫千<note n="0352004" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「千」，甲本作「一千」。</note>佛；</item>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a11"/><item id="itemW07p0352a1101">十五日齋，五道將軍下界<note n="0352005" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「下界」，底、甲本無，據文意補。</note>，念阿彌陀佛；</item>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a12"/><item id="itemW07p0352a1201">十八日齋，閻羅王天子下界，念地藏菩薩；</item>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a13"/><item id="itemW07p0352a1301">二十<note n="0352006" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「二十」，底本作「十二」，據甲本改。</note>三日齋，天大將軍下界，念大勢至菩薩；</item>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a14"/><item id="itemW07p0352a1401">二十四<note n="0352007" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「四」，甲本無。</note>日齋<note n="0352008" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「齋」，底本無。據甲本補。</note>，察命下界，念觀世音菩薩；</item>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a15"/><item id="itemW07p0352a1501">二十八日齋<note n="0352009" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「齋」，底、甲本無，據文意補。</note>，太山府君下界，念盧舍那佛；</item>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a16"/><item id="itemW07p0352a1601">二<note n="0352010" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「二」，甲本作「八」。</note>十九日齋，四天王下界，念藥王藥上<note n="0352011" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「藥上」，底、甲本無，據文意補。</note>菩薩；</item>
<pb ed="W" id="W07.0064c.0353a" n="0353a"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0353a01"/><item id="itemW07p0353a0101">三十日<note n="0353001" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「日」，甲本無。</note>齋，大<note n="0353002" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「大」，底、甲本作「念大」，據文意刪。</note>梵王下界，念釋迦牟尼佛。</item></list>
<lb ed="W" n="0353a02"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0353a03"/><p id="pW07p0353a0301">〔錄文完〕</p></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>
